Day 1 Mini-Project By Josh Ivanhoe and Jiong Wei Lua

Visualisations

Column

For price per person, we looked at the mean by neighbourhood of all booked rentals over the course the year, to ensure there was demand at the listings price. For review score, we simply calculated the mean by neighbourhood of all listings.

Column

For both review score and price, there appears to be positive correlation between nearby neighbourhoods, at least qualitatively. It is interesting to note there is complete agreement between our two metrics as to which areas are the most interesting.
